title: How do I transfer files between my HUAWEI MediaPad T1 8.0 and a Mac?
answer:
1.l Download and install Android File Transfer to your Mac from http://www.android.com/filetransfer/ or a third-party website.

1.l Connect your HUAWEI MediaPad T1 8.0 to the Mac using a USB cable. 

1.l Start Android File Transfer. You can then transfer files between your HUAWEI MediaPad T1 8.0 and the Mac.
